title: Chainsaw Sally [2004 - USA] indie comedy horror
description:
Chainsaw Sally (2004 - USA)

Comedy / Horror / Thriller

Production Companies: Forbidden Pictures | It Came From Planet X | Redfield Arts
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0385592/


Budget: $40,000 estimated

At the age of 10 years Sally had witnessed the brutal murder of her parents. Over some years the shock resulted in her developing a split personality. Now, by day, Sally is a mild-mannered librarian quick to hush those who get a little too loud in her quiet library. But by night, Sally turns into a chainsaw-wielding vixen quick to permanently quiet those who have wronged her, or her library.

Chainsaw Sally is fun and the film not only features cameos by Gunnar Hansen (Leatherface) and Herschell Gordon Lewis (Godfather of Gore), but it has also inspired a web series, The Chainsaw Sally Show.
